data.description: This House is Ready for you to make it a HOME!!! Beautiful Red Brick House in St Johns Landing. Fantastic Boating Community that hosts many Social Events.  This Spacious home has 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms! There is 2 Master Suites plus a game room. Ready to Entertain with open floor plan on ground level. Plenty of space to park in the pull through driveway with a 3 car garage. Tile through out the house and beautiful hardwood stairs. Double balconies on the second floor to accent the grand entry.  Private Boat Ramp to St. Johns River, Tennis Courts with Pickleball, Pool and Clubhouse only a short walk. Roof permitted in 2015, one HVAC 2021. House uses Electric Appliances but equipped to transfer to Gas.
